| 阶段1 | 骨架：只调用 Planner + Executor | Planner, Executor, Memory |
| 阶段2 | 增加：Risk + Report + Chart | RiskEngine, ReportBuilder, ChartBuilder |
| 阶段3 | 增加：Forecast + Scoring | ForecastEngine, ScoringEngine |
| 阶段4 | 增加：Decision + Rule + Action | DecisionEngine, RuleEngine, ActionEngine |
| 阶段5 | 增加：Event + Scheduler | EventBus, Scheduler |

每个阶段 Orchestrator 的 `run()` 方法逐步扩展，未实现的模块用空操作替代。

