### 条件操作符

| 操作符 | 说明 | 示例 |
|--------|------|------|
| `>` | 大于 | `{"field": "overdue_amount", "operator": ">", "value": 0}` |
| `>=` | 大于等于 | `{"field": "score", "operator": ">=", "value": 90}` |
| `<` | 小于 | `{"field": "confidence", "operator": "<", "value": 0.5}` |
| `<=` | 小于等于 | - |
| `==` | 等于 | `{"field": "status", "operator": "==", "value": "expired"}` |
| `in` | 包含于 | `{"field": "level", "operator": "in", "value": ["high", "medium"]}` |
| `contains` | 包含 | `{"field": "message", "operator": "contains", "value": "逾期"}` |

### 规则分类

| category | 说明 | 使用引擎 |
|----------|------|---------|
| risk | 风险识别规则 | RiskEngine |
| decision | 决策生成规则 | DecisionEngine |
| action | 动作执行规则 | ActionEngine |
| scoring | 评分规则 | ScoringEngine |
| notification | 通知触发规则 | Notifier |

